WEBVTT

00:02:59.236 --> 00:03:02.238
There were lines
of bodies laid in the street.

00:03:02.282 --> 00:03:04.551
And there was blood
all over the pavements.

00:03:05.908 --> 00:03:10.146
The following day,
President Yanukovych fled Ukraine.

00:03:10.146 --> 00:03:11.904
In all, three months of protests

00:03:11.929 --> 00:03:15.373
resulted in more than 120 confirmed dead

00:03:15.398 --> 00:03:16.920
and many more missing.

00:03:17.913 --> 00:03:19.956
History unfolded quickly,

00:03:19.956 --> 00:03:22.377
but celebration remained
elusive in Maidan.

00:03:23.488 --> 00:03:26.289
As the days passed
in Kiev's central square,

00:03:26.289 --> 00:03:27.828
streams of armed fighters

00:03:27.828 --> 00:03:31.254
were joined by tens of thousands
of ordinary people,